UPDATE secondary_sources SET enriched_text = 'Concepts: arrest purpose, interrogation, detention power, s4 Detention and Interrogation Act, right to silence

This chunk covers the principle that police cannot arrest simply for furthering investigation and notes Tasmanian statutory detention power.

